    {
      "id": "legend-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 960,
      "y": 920,
      "width": 180,
      "height": 250,
      "text": "Traffic Types:\n\n→ HTTP/Bolt (7474/7687)\n   Client access via Public LB\n\n⟷ RAFT (7000)\n   Direct pod-to-pod\n   consensus protocol\n\n⟷ Discovery (6000)\n   Cluster formation\n   via Internal LB\n\nNSG Rules:\n  Allow TCP 7000\n  between pod subnets",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "version": 2,
