      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Traffic Types:\n\n→ HTTP/Bolt (7474/7687)\n   Client access via Public LB\n\n⟷ RAFT (7000)\n   Direct pod-to-pod\n   consensus protocol\n\n⟷ Discovery (6000)\n   Cluster formation\n   via Internal LB\n\nNSG Rules:\n  Allow TCP 7000\n  between pod subnets",
